				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Julia sets and Mandelbrot sets are calculated with the same recurrence relation
<br />
<br />z[n+1] = z[n]^2 + c
<br />
<br />For the Mandlebrot set, z[0] = 0 and c varies over the entire complex plane.
<br />
<br />For Julia sets, a specific complex value c is selected, and z[0] varies over the entire complex plane.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

						<table width="100%" cellspacing="0">
